  <description>
    <p>The Legend of Edgar is a 2D platform game.
      Your hero must save his dad from the hands of the evil sorcerer.
      To help Edgar in his mission you must to walk around a big world, solve
      puzzles and kill a lot of powerful enemies.</p>
    <p>A great adventure awaits for you!</p>
  </description>
